/*
 * Primavera — Spanish landing page (florista-washington-heights)
 */{
  "sections": {
    "hero": {
      "type": "hero",
      "blocks": {
        "g": {
          "type": "group",
          "blocks": {
            "kicker": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Hablamos español · Tu florista en Washington Heights desde 2004</p>",
                "type_preset": "paragraph",
                "font": "var(--font-accent--family)",
                "case": "uppercase",
                "letter_spacing": "0.16em",
                "alignment": "left"
              }
            },
            "headline": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h1>Ramos frescos. Manos reales. Mismo día.</h1>",
                "type_preset": "h1",
                "font": "var(--font-heading--family)",
                "case": "none",
                "wrap": "balance"
              }
            },
            "sub": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Familia Sierra · 463 Fort Washington Ave · desde 2004. Tu florista de verdad — no un servicio 1-800 que envía tu pedido desde tres estados. Pide antes de las 2 PM y caminamos tu ramo a tu puerta el mismo día en Washington Heights, Hudson Heights e Inwood (10032, 10033, 10034 y 10040). Te mandamos una foto del ramo antes de que salga. Si algo no está bien, lo hacemos otra vez.</p>",
                "type_preset": "paragraph",
                "max_width": "narrow"
              }
            },
            "cta": {
              "type": "button",
              "settings": {
                "label": "Comprar ahora",
                "link": "shopify://collections/all",
                "style_class": "primary"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": ["kicker", "headline", "sub", "cta"],
          "settings": {
            "content_direction": "column",
            "horizontal_alignment": "flex-start",
            "gap": 16,
            "width": "custom",
            "custom_width": 55,
            "padding-block-start": 80,
            "padding-block-end": 80,
            "padding-inline-start": 48,
            "padding-inline-end": 48
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["g"],
      "settings": {
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "section_height": "large"
      }
    },
    "ocasiones": {
      "type": "collection-links",
      "blocks": {
        "h": {
          "type": "_inline-collection-title",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Ramos para cada momento</h2>",
            "alignment": "center",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "font": "var(--font-heading--family)"
          }
        },
        "cumple": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "birthday", "label": "Cumpleaños" } },
        "aniv": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "anniversary", "label": "Aniversario" } },
        "simpatia": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "sympathy", "label": "Condolencias" } },
        "porque": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "just-because", "label": "Solo porque sí" } },
        "quince": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "quinceanera", "label": "Quinceañera" } },
        "madres": { "type": "_collection-link", "settings": { "collection": "dia-de-las-madres", "label": "Día de las Madres" } }
      },
      "block_order": ["h", "cumple", "aniv", "simpatia", "porque", "quince", "madres"],
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-1",
        "section_width": "page-width",
        "padding-block-start": 64,
        "padding-block-end": 32
      }
    },
    "promesa": {
      "type": "media-with-content",
      "blocks": {
        "h": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Te enviamos una foto antes de salir.</h2>",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "font": "var(--font-heading--family)",
            "case": "none"
          }
        },
        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Cada arreglo lo fotografiamos antes de que salga de la tienda en la 187 con Fort Washington. Sabes exactamente qué llega a la puerta de Mami — sin sorpresas, sin sustitutos, sin promesas vacías. Y si prefieres, pasa por la tienda y te lo armamos al momento.</p>",
            "type_preset": "paragraph"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["h", "body"],
      "settings": {
        "color_scheme": "scheme-3",
        "section_width": "full-width",
        "media_position": "left",
        "media_width": 50
      }
    }
  },
  "order": ["hero", "ocasiones", "promesa"]
}
